<h4 class="heading"><span class="type">Paragraph</span></h4>
<p>You have surely noticed that the calculations you had to do to evaluate the integrals in <a href="" class="xref" data-knowl="./knowl/TrickySubstitution1.html" title="Checkpoint 1.10">Problem 1.10</a> were quite intricate. Not hard, <i class="foreign">per se,</i> but there were a lot of steps and at each point you had to draw on just the right tool from Algebra, or Trigonometry, or Differential Calculus.</p>
<span class="incontext"><a href="section-4.html#p-69" class="internal">in-context</a></span>
